{"id":387635,"date":[{"year":1959,"month":4,"day":5}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"82","ytitle":"","mtitle":"一剪梅　已亥清明","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>建恺</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1959\\04\\5945031401.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>寒食清明放眼看:春满江南，万世鲜妍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乍晴乍雨好耕田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沃野连天麦浪无边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壅土堆肥穀雨前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁岁争先岁岁丰年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平凡劳动着先鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越是平凡，越尊严。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建恺</FONT>"}]}